819
01:07:57,739 --> 01:08:01,856
Oh, I don't know... a little after 10:00, maybe 1:00.

820
01:08:02,114 --> 01:08:02,887
10:00 to 1:00.

821
01:08:03,914 --> 01:08:07,961
I was wondering if he'd gone home, and then I found him passed out on the couch.

822
01:08:08,765 --> 01:08:13,586
He told me I thought you were gone, I was sad.

823
01:08:15,093 --> 01:08:17,797
He pretested to be cool.

824
01:08:19,266 --> 01:08:24,687
I even went to a hotel with him, but that was stupid.

825
01:08:24,899 --> 01:08:26,516
You left here together?

826
01:08:26,883 --> 01:08:27,375
Yes.

827
01:08:28,102 --> 01:08:29,953
Well, didn't SENO have a car at that time?

828
01:08:30,070 --> 01:08:32,477
Yes he had.
Nishiaki's car.

829
01:08:34,546 --> 01:08:37,531
Nishiaki's car?
You sure?

830
01:08:56,570 --> 01:09:04,734
I would like to propose a toast to the prosperity of the bride and groom and their families.

831
01:09:05,086 --> 01:09:06,820
Congratulation!

832
01:09:10,878 --> 01:09:13,097
