833
01:09:13,511 --> 01:09:14,550
Again?

834
01:09:16,613 --> 01:09:18,339
He's kind of rude.

835
01:09:23,303 --> 01:09:25,538
Still no end to the party?

836
01:09:26,522 --> 01:09:28,358
I need you.

837
01:09:29,092 --> 01:09:31,022
No way.
I'm a doctor.

838
01:09:32,130 --> 01:09:35,528
Hello, please... I made your marriage happen, just like we promised.

839
01:09:37,911 --> 01:09:39,880
I'm about to give her another dose of anesthesia.

840
01:09:44,548 --> 01:09:46,462
Oh you're still here.

841
01:09:47,298 --> 01:09:49,189
I have to work.

842
01:09:49,939 --> 01:09:51,298
Hello?

843
01:09:52,962 --> 01:09:54,267
Sachiko Kasahara?

844
01:09:55,040 --> 01:09:56,329
From Yoshii

845
01:09:56,970 --> 01:09:58,790
She's not here

846
01:09:59,404 --> 01:10:02,310
She hasn't visited us.

847
01:10:02,779 --> 01:10:04,123
See you.

848
01:10:05,752 --> 01:10:08,025
I'm about to leave, so you guys should go, too.

849
01:10:22,771 --> 01:10:24,045
You look so nice.

850
01:10:26,014 --> 01:10:27,975
Oh Dr.Nishiaki

851
01:10:38,031 --> 01:10:38,796
Seno

852
01:10:40,062 --> 01:10:44,734
I'm so glad you took the time to come.

853
01:10:44,759 --> 01:10:46,249
You're in danger.

854
01:10:46,851 --> 01:10:47,937
Congratulations.

855
01:10:51,914 --> 01:10:53,203
Anesthesia is working?

856
01:10:54,835 --> 01:10:55,804
Anyway, please come right away

857
01:10:56,781 --> 01:10:58,656
Just wait until this party's over.

858
01:10:58,820 --> 01:10:59,601


859
01:10:59,671 --> 01:11:01,562
Another an hour.

860
01:11:01,938 --> 01:11:03,626
We don't have time.

861
01:11:08,313 --> 01:11:09,837
Please think about the location.

862
