874
01:12:07,560 --> 01:12:09,521
And in the middle of a Christmas party too!

875
01:12:11,091 --> 01:12:13,576
But tomorrow I'm flying to Paris with Reiko.

876
01:12:13,873 --> 01:12:16,271
So everything's fine with me.

877
01:12:16,296 --> 01:12:17,498
Then what about me?

878
01:12:17,763 --> 01:12:18,560
Up to you.

879
01:12:20,295 --> 01:12:22,802
By my calculations, we don't owe each other anything.

880
01:12:26,498 --> 01:12:28,810
What if you solve the problem alone?

881
01:12:33,006 --> 01:12:36,053
If I could do it on my own, I wouldn't have asked for your help in the first place.

882
01:12:37,201 --> 01:12:41,318
Yes, you can. Make the best of what you do.

883
01:12:42,443 --> 01:12:45,076
You know, you could do her face and dig in the ocean.

884
01:12:46,412 --> 01:12:49,498
